<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>E</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vawlei nih, harnak an pek lai, Siseh ttih hlah uh ka tei cang
 Teitu thawnnak kan lei a ttan ah cun, Vawlei zawtnak fahnak tilet, Chum le Minmei bang zam hmangseh
 An ttian dih lai Jesuh min thawnnakin.

[C1]
   Jesuh min sunglawi an theihah, Rulhreu thawnnak
   Cu an zam dih, Van lei zoh law na nunnak Bawipa pe
   Thihnak a tei Vawlei a tei, Mitcaw kebei mi hna damnak
   A kut cu zumhnak in i tlaih, na dam lai.

[V2]
 Zawtnak ruangah kum zeizah dah, Lung rethei le harsatnak in
 Sawmthum kumriat mizengpa a dam cang, Thleidan ngeilo
 Jesuh dawtnak, Kan nih ca zongah kan damnak
 Na lung dong hlah Jesuh an damter lai.

[V3]
 Kum hleihnih chung thi a chuakmi, Jesuh puanki
 Tawnghin a dam, Zumhnak in thlacam law a puanki tawng
 Lung awtawmnak ngei hin hlah mu, Ai thleng ballo Pathian
 Thawnnak, Thawnginn na zawtnak cu a dam cang lai.

[V4]
 Hi zaihla sung ngaimi unau, Jesuh minin na zawtnak kha, Na kut in tawng law zumhnak in thlacam
 Na lungthin dihlak in Au law, David fapa ka
 Zangfah tuah, A kut thawnnak thawngin, na dam cang lai.</lyrics>
<title>JESUH MIN SUNGLAWI</title>
</song>